    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"let the curtain fall...\" that's exactly it. but the thing is, even if i stop performing, there's nothing underneath. there's no version of me that actually fits into this world. it just feels like a loop of constant discomfort that's never gonna end. like i'm just wasting space.",
